1. Ahmedabad: Data Science & AI Hub
Ahmedabad is home to specialized AI firms and data-focused product companies. 
fxis.ai (F(x) Data Labs) – Widely recognized as a dedicated data science firm specializing in Machine Learning, NLP, and Generative AI.
SPEC INDIA – An established enterprise software provider with deep expertise in Business Intelligence (BI) and data analytics.
Maruti Techlabs – Focuses on artificial intelligence, data engineering, and building data-driven custom software.
Crest Data – Specializes in data analytics, cybersecurity, and cloud-based data solutions.
Tatvic Analytics – A leader in marketing and web analytics, providing advanced data insights for global brands.
GrowExx – Actively hires for data scientist roles, focusing on model optimization and AI research.
Ecolibrium Energy – Provides predictive asset intelligence and industrial energy analytics.
Adani Digital Labs – The digital arm of Adani Group, focusing on large-scale consumer data analytics. 

2. Gandhinagar: GIFT City & Enterprise Analytics 
Gandhinagar, particularly GIFT City, hosts large multinational corporations with extensive data science divisions.
TCS (Tata Consultancy Services) – Employs large teams for data science, predictive modeling, and enterprise analytics.
HCLTech – Offers AI-enabled digital transformation and data engineering services.
Cognizant – Focuses on automated data workflows and AI-driven business insights.
DRC Systems – An IT firm building RAG pipelines and proprietary AI solutions.
Infividhya – Specifically listed as a provider of dedicated data science and analysis services in Gandhinagar. 

3. Kadi: Industrial & Data Management Services
In Kadi, data roles are primarily found in industrial IT support and data processing centers.
Prince It Info Tech Solution – Offers IT consultancy and is linked to data center operations.
Jayveer Business Solution – Provides data management and Android-based data solutions.
Compuman Infotech – A local provider of data processing services.
Corbital Communication – An IT service provider that manages infrastructure and data connectivity.
White Pearl It Solution – Handles custom software development and data-related applications. 
